data.description:
Welcome to your new home sweet home at 143 Kale Court! This charming property offers 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, and it has recently undergone a stunning transformation. With fresh paint, new flooring, and updated appliances, this home has received a bright new look that is sure to impress.

Conveniently located just minutes away from the front gate, this property provides easy access to all the amenities and activities that the area has to offer. Additionally, it falls within the highly regarded Waynesville school district, ensuring a quality education for your family.

Don't wait too long to make this house your home, as it is sure to attract a lot of attention. Check out our virtual tour! Schedule a viewing today and seize the opportunity to own this beautiful property at 143 Kale Court!
